- Synthesizing advisor findings into investment committee materials
- Tracking due diligence workstreams and critical path items
- Preparing Q&A logs and ensuring all material questions are addressed

*Technical & Operational Analysis:*
- Understanding asset technical specifications, capacity, and operational performance metrics
- Reviewing capital expenditure programs and asset condition assessments
- Assessing operational efficiency, maintenance requirements, and replacement capital needs
- Evaluating technology risks and obsolescence considerations
- Working with technical consultants to validate engineering assumptions

*Regulatory & Policy Analysis:*
- Understanding regulatory regimes (economic regulation, environmental regulation, licensing requirements)
- Analyzing rate-setting methodologies for regulated assets (building blocks, incentive regulation)
- Assessing regulatory risk and potential for adverse determinations
- Monitoring policy developments and their impact on asset value (renewable energy targets, climate policy)
- Reviewing regulatory submissions and determinations

*Investment Committee Materials:*
- Drafting investment committee papers synthesizing analysis and recommendations
- Preparing executive summaries highlighting key investment merits and risks
- Creating presentation materials with clear, compelling visuals
- Supporting senior team members in IC presentations and Q&A

*Portfolio Company Support:*
